init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Some blame the economy, others say it's because of a gender bias.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The reason the Dad mugs no longer said #1 was found out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mugs were a window into the dad's soul.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Now, there were some dads who did not have a #1 mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The #1 Dad Mug was for the dad who would never let his kids down.
